  "storyline": "# Storyline\n\n## Context\n\nT20 match outcomes hinge on phase-specific dynamics (Powerplay, Middle, Death) that flat match-level stats miss.\n\n## Workflow\n\nPhase-level EDA → feature engineering → multi-model classification → match-by-match outcome probabilities.\n\n## Technical Implementation\n\n- **EDA:** phase-level analysis with Pandas, surfacing scoring patterns consistent with public T20 research.\n- **Features:** 25+ features across team composition, player metrics, venue and conditions.\n- **Modeling:** Random Forest, Logistic Regression and SVM; Random Forest best at ~80.55% accuracy.\n\n## Outcomes\n\nTranslated outputs into match-by-match outcome probabilities framed for cricket-domain audiences against tactical decisions."
